-header-Club-NME-Eva-Pentel-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Mae-Muller-header-Club-NME-Eva-Pentel-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Mae-Muller-header-Club-NME-Eva-Pentel-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Mae-Muller-header-Club-NME-Eva-Pentel-1392x883.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Mae-Muller-header-Club-NME-Eva-Pentel-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/mae-muller">梅·穆勒 (Mae Muller)</a>于本周末在伦敦斯卡拉 (Scala) 与<a href="http://ladbrokeslive.co.uk/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Ladbrokes LIVE</a>合作的最新一期<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/club-nme">Club NME</a>节目中担任主角（4 月 12 日）。</p><p>在她今年的首场头条秀中，穆勒首次以时尚的方式重返舞台，首次演唱了她 2023 年专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/mae-muller-album-review-sorry-im-late-debut-radar-3504525">《对不起，我迟到了》</a>中的曲目。演出对象是熟悉每首歌词的家乡观众，演出涵盖了从粉丝最喜爱的《Work Like That》到她的巨制单曲《I Wrote A Song》，后者是英国 2023 年欧洲歌唱大赛的参赛作品。</p><p>观众还欣赏了流行音乐巨星<a href="/artists/self-esteem">Self Esteem</a>和变装偶像 Raven Mandella 的 DJ 表演，后者以色彩缤纷、充满活力的表演拉开了帷幕。穆勒演出结束后，“自尊”活动立即延续了派对气氛，这位水星奖提名艺术家将她最喜欢的俱乐部经典歌曲演绎到凌晨。 </p><figure id="attachment_3618026" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3618026" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3618026" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Club-NME-Mae-Muller-Eva-Pentel.jpg" alt="梅·穆勒 (Mae Muller) 在 NME 俱乐部" width="2000" height="1269" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Club-NME-Mae-Muller-Eva-Pentel.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Club-NME-Mae-Muller-Eva-Pentel-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Club-NME-Mae-Muller-Eva-Pentel-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Club-NME-Mae-Muller-Eva-Pentel-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Club-NME-Mae-Muller-Eva-Pentel-1392x883.jp